Here's how you can use this function in your code:

```javascript
// Assuming you have an element with id 'myElement' as root and an element with id 'myDragHandle' as drag handle
var root = document.getElementById('myElement');
var dragHandle = document.getElementById('myDragHandle');

// Call makeDraggable function with root element and drag handle element as arguments
