Please note that this function uses event listeners for 'mousedown', 'mousemove', and 'mouseup' events which means you don't have to manually add these event listeners in your HTML code. The function will automatically handle these events for you. 

Also note that this function does not handle cases where the drag handle is moved outside of its parent container or goes off-screen. You may want to add additional logic for these cases depending on your specific needs.

